%tr
  %th.label
    %label{:for=>"user_groups"} Groups
  %td.field
    - Group.find(:all).each do |group|
      %span.checkbox
        = check_box_tag "user[group_ids][]", group.id, @user.is_in?(group)
        = group.title
        %span.explanatory
          = group.description
  %td.help
    Groups give access to restricted pages on the public site.